Phone/right-wall window props Pico project.

Default pins:
- GPIO 14: reset button to GND, using internal pull-up
- GPIO 15: phone puzzle solved input
- GPIO 16: right-wall/window prop input

MQTT publish:
- escape/puzzle/phone/solved
- escape/puzzle/window/triggered
- escape/post/cubby/5/state = ready or completed

MQTT commands:
- escape/post/query
- escape/game/reset

When the local reset button is pressed, the Pico republishes its POST state.

Sensor inputs assume external pull-down wiring.
